requests.name: subscribe - call B218
requests.description:
"Subscribe a bank statement to one or more channels
 process for subscribing a bank statement to card SIA:
 -subscribe to receive a bank statement for the online channel
 -subscribe to receive a bank statement for the paper channel
 -subscribe to receive a bank statement for the online and paper channel

 process for subscribing a bank statement to card Equens:
 -subscribe to receive a bank statement for the online channel
 -subscribe to receive a bank statement for the online and paper channel

 The functionality SUBSCRIBE automaticaly  delete the previous channel and subscribe to new channel.
 For example if a cardholder is subscirbe for the card SIA to bank statement for the online and paper channel and asks to subscribe only online channel, the API  SUBSCRIBE , check the actual status, delete the paper channel, and subscribe to the online channel."
